<h4 id="fopen">fopen</h4>
<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">FILE *fopen(const char *filename, const
char* mode);</code>
    <ul>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">r</code> (ÂîØËÆÄÊ®°Âºè)</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">w</code> (ÂØ´ÂÖ•Ê®°Âºè„ÄÅÈï∑Â∫¶Ê≠∏Èõ∂)</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">a</code> (ÂØ´ÂÖ•Ê®°Âºè„ÄÅÈôÑÂä†)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h4 id="2-printf-sprintf-fprintf">2. printf, sprintf, fprintf</h4>
<p>%d, %o, %x, %c ,%s ,%f (float) ,%e (double) ,%g (double)</p>

<h4 id="3-scanf-fscanf-sscanf">3. scanf, fscanf, sscanf</h4>
